<!DOCTYPE html>

<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en">

<head>
  <meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8"/>
</head>

<body>
<table cellpadding='0' cellspacing='0' style="width: 700px; height: 394px;margin: auto; background: url('/image/email/airmail_all_bg.jpg') repeat #fbe9d1">
  <tr style="height: 350px">
    <td style="padding: 20px 0 0 30px;vertical-align: top;">
      <%= yield %>
    </td>
    <td style="width: 260px"></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 0 0 20px 30px;vertical-align: top;">
      <div class="small_bottom_text" style="vertical-align: bottom; color: #534731; font-size: 12px">
        <% if @language.present? && @language == 'ru' %>
            Вы можете отписаться проследовав по этой ссылке: <a href="<%= unsubscribe_from_blog_url(:id => @subscriber.id) %>" style="color: #346585">Отписаться!</a>
      <% else %>
            You can unsubscribe by this link: <a href="<%= unsubscribe_from_blog_url(:id => @subscriber.id) %>" style="color: #346585">Unsubscribe!</a>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </td>
    <td style="width: 260px"></td>
  </tr>
</table>
</body>
</html>
